---
// src/pages/docs/core/install.astro
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Install & Overview - Core">
  <div
    class="mb-4 text-sm font-mono text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest"
  >
    @elekcsv/core
  </div>

  <h1 class="mb-8 border-b-2 border-black pb-4">1.1 Install & Overview</h1>

  <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
    The <code>@elekcsv/core</code> is the foundational parsing engine. It is strictly
    headless, UI-agnostic, and relies on optimized, zero-allocation algorithms and
    dynamic V8 code generation (JIT) rather than polymorphic loops.
  </p>

  <h2>Installation</h2>
  <p>
    The core package is ideal for Node.js backends, workers, or if you prefer to
    build your own UI components from scratch.
  </p>

  <pre><code>npm install @elekcsv/core
# or
yarn add @elekcsv/core
# or
pnpm add @elekcsv/core</code></pre>

  <h2>Why Core?</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong class="text-black">Dynamic Parsing Pipeline:</strong> Instead of generic
      regex matching, `createParser` dynamically generates a Javascript function
      unique to your specific schema.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong class="text-black">Zero-Allocation Data Structures:</strong> Reduces
      garbage collection pauses during heavy multi-megabyte streams.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong class="text-black">Fuzzy Column Mapping:</strong> Handle "Email Address",
      "email", and "E-mail" automatically with locale-aware distance algorithms.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong class="text-black">State Machine (`ImporterMachine`):</strong> Process
      data in batches and manage stream lifecycle with an event-driven architecture.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mt-16 flex justify-end">
    <a
      href="/docs/core/basic"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-md text-sm font-medium hover:bg-neutral-800 no-underline! transition-colors"
      style="text-decoration:none;"
    >
      Next: Basic Usage
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        ><path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
